------ Test: support group by with enum
SELECT struct('a' AS discriminant, struct(t1.value AS a) AS a, CAST(NULL AS STRUCT<b INT>) AS b, CAST(NULL AS STRUCT<c INT>) AS c) AS _1, count(CAST(1 AS INT)) AS _2 FROM t1 GROUP BY t1.value
------ end

------ Test: support group by with nested option
